  {
    name: 'Partnership Excellence',
    text: 'What an incredible journey we have had together! During the last year you have improved your performance delivery considerably.',
  },
  {
    name: 'Team Inspiration',
    text: "You bring countless energy and creativity into everything you do & it's inspiring to see how you juggle it all â€“ with ambition and resilience!",
  },
